query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!" FROM attorneys
        WHERE court_id = $1
          AND (
            lower(first_name) LIKE $2
            OR lower(last_name) LIKE $2
            OR lower(bar_number) LIKE $2
            OR lower(email) LIKE $2
            OR lower(COALESCE(firm_name, '')) LIKE $2
          )
